{
    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-template-js",
    "path": "/css/border-radius/",
    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"3faac376-8d3e-5ab2-aace-1fce4e055fc4","html":"<h2 id=\"-border-radius\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-border-radius\" aria-label=\" border radius permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 border-radius</h2>\n<p>요소의 모서리를 둥글게 깎는 것을 의미한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: <code class=\"language-text\">0</code> - 둥글게 없음</li>\n<li>단위: px, em, vw 등 단위로 지정</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>해당 요소의 각 모서리에 반지름이 10px 인 동그라미를(정 원을) 배치한 후,<br />\n요소에서 동그라미를 벗어나는 부분을 삭제하는 원리이다.</p>\n<br />\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 10px 0 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">왼쪽 위</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">오른쪽 위</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">오른쪽 아래</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">왼쪽 아래</code> 의<br />\n시계 방향 순서로 적용할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-border-radius\">💙 border-radius</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"💙 border-radius 요소의 모서리를 둥글게 깎는 것을 의미한다. 기본값:  - 둥글게 없음 단위: px, em, vw 등 단위로 지정 해당 요소의 각 모서리에 반지름이 10px 인 동그라미를(정 원을) 배치한 후,\n요소에서 동그라미를 벗어나는 부분을 삭제하는 원리이다.  -  -  -  의\n시계 방향 순서로 적용할 수 있다. 💙 border-radius","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.10","title":"[CSS] border-radius","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/border-radius/"}},"next":{"id":"90d0e36d-47f3-549c-bbf9-3f2f5f303861","html":"<h2 id=\"-border\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-border\" aria-label=\" border permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 border</h2>\n<p>요소의 <strong>테두리 선</strong>을 지정하는 <strong>단축 속성</strong>이다.<br />\n테두리 선의 두께가 늘어날수록 요소의 크기가 커진다.</p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"1-border-width\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-border-width\" aria-label=\"1 border width permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. border-width</h3>\n<p>요소 테두리 <strong>선의 두께</strong>를 의미한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: <code class=\"language-text\">medium</code></li>\n<li>단위: px, em, % 등 <strong>단위로 지정</strong></li>\n<li>thin(얇은 두께), thick(두꺼운 두께) 값이 있지만 잘 사용하지 않는다.</li>\n<li>border 라는 단축 속성의 <strong>개별 속성</strong>이면서,<br />\n각 방향별로 한번에 적용가능한 <strong>단축 속성</strong>이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px 20px 30px 40px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"2-border-style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-border-style\" aria-label=\"2 border style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. border-style</h3>\n<p>요소 테두리 <strong>선의 종류</strong>를 의미한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: <code class=\"language-text\">none</code> - 선 없음</li>\n<li><strong>solid</strong>: 실선 (일반 선)</li>\n<li><strong>dotted</strong>: 점선 (… .)</li>\n<li><strong>dashed</strong>: 파선 (- - - -)</li>\n<li>double: 두 줄 선</li>\n<li>groove: 홈이 파여있는 모양</li>\n<li>ridge: 솟은 모양 (groove 의 반대)</li>\n<li>inset: 요소 전체가 들어간 모양</li>\n<li>outset: 요소 전체가 나온 모양</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"3-border-color\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-border-color\" aria-label=\"3 border color permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. border-color</h3>\n<p>요소 테두리 <strong>선의 색상</strong>을 지정하는 <strong>단축 속성</strong>을 의미한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: <code class=\"language-text\">black</code></li>\n<li>색상: 선의 색상</li>\n<li>transparent: 투명</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> black white orange yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"4-단축-속성-예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%EB%8B%A8%EC%B6%95-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"4 단축 속성 예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 단축 속성 예시</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> medium none black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>각각의 기본값을 단축 속성으로 사용한 것이다.<br />\n선의 종류가 none 이기 때문에 출력되지 않는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"5-기타-속성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"5 기타 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. 기타 속성</h3>\n<p>요소의 테두리 선을 지정하는 기타 속성들이다.<br />\n방향 별로 세밀하게 속성들을 설정한 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border-방향</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 두께 종류 색상<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-방향-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 두께<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-방향-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 종류<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-방향-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 색상<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"6-색상-표현\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%83%89%EC%83%81-%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"6 색상 표현 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 색상 표현</h3>\n<p>색을 사용하는 모든 속성에 적용 가능한 색상 표현을 의미한다.</p>\n<p>(1) 색상 이름</p>\n<ul>\n<li>브라우저에서 제공하는 색상 이름</li>\n<li>브라우저에 따라 달라지기 때문에 정확하지 않다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">red</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">tomato</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">royalblue</code> …</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<p>(2) Hex 색상코드</p>\n<ul>\n<li>16진수 색상 (Hexadecimal Colors)</li>\n<li>가장 많이 사용하는 방식이다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">#000</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">#FFFFFF</code></li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<p>(3) RGB</p>\n<ul>\n<li>빛의 삼원색</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">rgb(255, 255, 255)</code> // rgb 는 함수!</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<p>(4) RGBA</p>\n<ul>\n<li>빛의 삼원색 + 투명도</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)</code> // rgba 도 함수!</li>\n<li>1, 2, 3 번째는 RGB, 마지막 4번째는 투명도이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-border\">💙 border</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-border-width\">1. border-width</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-border-style\">2. border-style</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-border-color\">3. border-color</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-%EB%8B%A8%EC%B6%95-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">4. 단축 속성 예시</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#5-%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\">5. 기타 속성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#6-%EC%83%89%EC%83%81-%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84\">6. 색상 표현</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.10","title":"[CSS] 테두리 선(border)과 색상표현","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/border/"}},"prev":{"id":"8b76012f-c488-5ff3-8214-1304fffa96f0","html":"<h2 id=\"-box-sizing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-box-sizing\" aria-label=\" box sizing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 box-sizing</h2>\n<p>요소의 크기 계산 기준을 지정하는 것이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: <code class=\"language-text\">content-box</code>- 요소의 내용(content)으로 크기를 계산한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">border-box</code>: 요소의 내용 + padding + border 로 크기를 계산한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"1-content-box\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-content-box\" aria-label=\"1 content box permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. content-box</h3>\n<p>요소의 <code class=\"language-text\">내용</code>(content)으로 크기를 계산한다.<br /></p>\n<p>padding, border 같이 요소의 크기가 커지는 속성이 적용되었을 때,<br />\n원하는 정확한 수치를 위해서는 width, height 를 <strong>수동으로 계산해서 명시</strong>해줘야 하는 단점이 있을 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 실제 가로 너비: 1 + 20 + 100 + 20 + 1 = 142px */</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"1-border-box\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-border-box\" aria-label=\"1 border box permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. border-box</h3>\n<p>요소의 <code class=\"language-text\">내용</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">padding</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">border</code> 로 크기를 계산한다.<br /></p>\n<p>직접 명시한 width, height <strong>사이즈를 유지</strong>하면서,<br />\n내부에 padding, border 가 <strong>자동으로 계산</strong>되어 들어간다.<br /></p>\n<p>따라서 width, height 를 <strong>수동으로 계산해서 명시</strong>해줘야 하는 불편함을 겪지 않도록 해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> border-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 실제 가로 너비: 100px */</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-box-sizing\">💙 box-sizing</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-content-box\">1. content-box</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-border-box\">1. border-box</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.10","title":"[CSS] box-sizing","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/box-sizing/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://autumnly1007.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"autumnly1007/autumnly1007.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css/border-radius/","nextSlug":"/css/border/","prevSlug":"/css/box-sizing/"}},
